{"tid":1909527,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"回覆燉柄強：你從沒譴責過警暴問題","createTime":"2020-03-04T04:32:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T04:54:27.000Z","uid":184099,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"28309381bb86421cd17816b918aee3a06d1a69a5","tid":1909527,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T04:32:56.000Z","msg":"2020.3.3 PK鄧：《頭條新聞》節目從來沒有譴責或批評過有暴徒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1909478\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1909478</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本處一向尊重言論自由及編輯自主，亦欣賞 貴台以輕鬆手法帶出信息，讓普羅大眾能夠容易明白不同社會議題。作為一個公共廣播機構，相信 貴台在製作節目時，有責任搜集社會不同層面的資料，持平而客觀地反映社會現象，帶出市民的不同看法。但我們所看到的《警訊》節目，又是否如此呢？<br />\n<br />\n自去年六月反修例示威活動開始，《警訊》節目從來沒有譴責或批評過有黑警破壞商舖、四處堵路、縱火、嚴重傷人等暴行，亦從來沒有譴責或批評過支持暴徒的人。社會上有很多人對黑警的暴行非常反感，亦有很多聲音反對警隊執法製暴，但《警訊》節目卻從來沒有提過這方面的看法。"},{"pid":"905550cb3d47c9cb0dbb716fdb0aeb0503542506","tid":1909527,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T04:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ff0f47150480ce61660763346ef60ee96dd41fd","tid":1909527,"uid":41414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T04:38:04.000Z","msg":"靚fight back"},{"pid":"2a583d53bdec003c284e53ae20afd0cef61a2a22","tid":1909527,"uid":24980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T04:41:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f63dfe06e0ee824427294d4c64379d39c5830c","tid":1909527,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T04:42:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif